WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.075
Kvadratni tortadigan ba’zi kodlar.

00:00:03.075 --> 00:00:06.980
Xuddi shu satrlarni qayta-qayta ishlatayotganimizga e’tibor bering,

00:00:06.980 --> 00:00:10.055
va bu faqat to‘rt tomonli kvadrat uchun.

00:00:10.055 --> 00:00:14.085
Agar biz yuz tomonli shakl chizmoqchi bo‘lsak nima bo‘ladi?

00:00:14.085 --> 00:00:17.820
Bu juda ko‘p ish va kerak emas ekan.

00:00:17.820 --> 00:00:19.829
for sikli yordamida

00:00:19.829 --> 00:00:22.050
biz istalgancha tomonli shaklni chizishimiz mumkin

00:00:22.050 --> 00:00:25.270
va u kod faqat uch qatorni oladi.

00:00:25.270 --> 00:00:27.210
for siklini yaratish uchun

00:00:27.210 --> 00:00:28.975
biz bu kabi chiziqdan boshlaymiz;

00:00:28.975 --> 00:00:31.990
tomonlar uchun [1, 2,

00:00:31.990 --> 00:00:42.420
3, 4]: keyin biz uni sikllash yoki takrorlashni xohlagan kod bilan birga olamiz.

00:00:42.420 --> 00:00:47.590
Ushbu chiziqlarni to‘rtta bo‘shliqqa o‘ng tomonga siljitish (indent) orqali qanday qilib ularni ajratganimizga e’tibor bering.

00:00:47.590 --> 00:00:51.145
Shunday qilib, biz ushbu qatorlar sikl ichida ekanligini ko‘rsatamiz.

00:00:51.145 --> 00:00:55.850
Boshqacha aytganda, bu takrorlanadigan qatorlar.

00:00:55.850 --> 00:00:59.235
Shunday qilib, ushbu kod bir necha bor ishlaydi,

00:00:59.235 --> 00:01:00.925
lekin necha marta?

00:01:00.925 --> 00:01:06.740
Xo‘sh, ushbu chiziqdagi yana to‘rt narsaga e’tibor bering.

00:01:06.740 --> 00:01:09.920
Aslida, bu 

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:13.835
ushbu ro‘yxatdagi har bir narsa uchun kod bir marta ishga tushirilishini aytadi.

00:01:13.835 --> 00:01:16.300
Ro‘yxatda to‘rtta element mavjudligi sababli,

00:01:16.300 --> 00:01:18.795
sikl to‘rt marta ishlaydi.

00:01:18.795 --> 00:01:20.435
Ushbu aniq sikl uchun,

00:01:20.435 --> 00:01:23.320
ro‘yxatdagi narsalar aslida muhim emas.

00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:26.930
Biz bu raqamlarni o‘zgartirishimiz yoki hatto ularni satrlar bilan almashtirishimiz mumkin.

00:01:26.930 --> 00:01:30.710
Yana, sikl ro‘yxatdagi har bir element uchun bir martadan ishlaydi

00:01:30.710 --> 00:01:35.360
va ro‘yxatdagi to‘rtta element mavjudligi sababli, sikl to‘rt marta ishlaydi.

